  "title": "Staff Nurse – Oncology (Novena) 💉#HHLT",
  "description": "<p></p><p>Location: Novena</p><p>Salary: Up to $5,500</p><p>Working Hours:</p><p>Mon – Fri (8:30am – 5:30pm)</p><p>Alternate Saturday<br /><br /></p><p></p><p></p><p>Job Scope</p><p>Deliver nursing care to oncology patients in outpatient settings</p><p>Assist in chemotherapy treatments and related procedures</p><p>Monitor patient conditions and manage treatment side effects</p><p>Provide patient education, emotional support, and follow-up care</p><p>Maintain accurate clinical documentation and records<br /><br /></p><p></p><p></p><p>Requirements</p><p>Min Diploma in Nursing; SNB registered</p><p>Prior Oncology experience; 2+ years hospital/clinic experience<br /></p><p><br /></p><p></p><p>If interested, please email me at biopharma@recruitexpress.com.sg or telegram @alexgohhl</p><p></p><p>➖</p><p>Alex Goh Hock Leong</p><p>(CEI.No: R1763413 l Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Life Science) | 99C4599)</p>",
